# SECURITY_DEPS_LEDGER

> Live authoritative copy generated by `scripts/deps_audit.py --write`.
> Initial template — populated entries only after a successful schema-validated run.

## Schema

Each row matches one row of `scripts/deps_audit.py:RowEntry` dataclass:

| Field           | Type          | Notes |
|-----------------|---------------|-------|
| `ghsa_id`       | string        | Must match `^GHSA-[a-z0-9]{4}-[a-z0-9]{4}-[a-z0-9]{4}$` |
| `severity`      | string        | exact: `LOW`, `MODERATE`, `HIGH`, `CRITICAL` |
| `cvss`          | float \| null | 0.0–10.0 |
| `ecosystem`     | string        | exact: `cargo`, `npm`, `pip` |
| `pkg`           | string        | crate / package name |
| `introduced`    | string        | semver-like string from GHSA |
| `fixed`         | string \| null | first patched version, or `null` |
| `owner`         | string        | GitHub handle of assignable human |
| `sla_tier`      | string        | exact: `SLA0`, `SLA1`, `SLA2`, `SLA3` |
| `action`        | string        | exact: `bump`, `monitor`, `replace`, `accept` |
| `pr_or_commit`  | string \| null | URL of remediation |
| `notes`         | string        | free-form |

## Index

| ghsa_id | severity | ecosystem | pkg | sla_tier | action | pr_or_commit | notes |
|---------|----------|-----------|-----|----------|--------|--------------|-------|

